{"type":"message","id":"be18c034","parentId":"89259065","timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:22:41.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The workspace is already in Dropbox at `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace`. So both Desktop (Windows/WSL) and Mac can access the same Dropbox folder. On Mac, the Dropbox folder path would be something like `/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace`.\n\nSo the solution is:\n1. On Mac, install OpenClaw\n2. Point the workspace to the Dropbox folder\n3. Both machines will share the same memory, SOUL, AGENTS, etc.\n\nNow let me figure out the exact path on Mac. The user has Dropbox on Mac, so the workspace would be at something like `/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace` on Mac.\n\n\nI'll walk through what needs to happen on the Mac side: install OpenClaw via npm, then configure the workspace path to point to that Dropbox location so both machines stay in sync.\n","thinkingSignature":"4c52f79700e4954f2ecfc81919f71a2b5482099ff377beca055b44a92f854d70"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🧑🏼‍💻 ง่ายมากครับ! **workspace อยู่ใน Dropbox อยู่แล้ว** (`/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace`)\n\nMac กับ Desktop ก็แค่ใช้ folder เดียวกัน!\n\n**ขั้นตอนบน Mac:**\n\n1. **ติดตั้ง OpenClaw:**\n```bash\nnpm install -g openclaw@latest\n```\n\n2. **สร้าง symlink ให้ workspace ชี้ไป Dropbox:**\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw\nln -s ~/Dropbox/owen-workspace ~/.openclaw/workspace\n```\n\n3. **เริ่มต้น:**\n```bash\nopenclaw onboard --install-daemon\n```\n\n**ผลลัพธ์:**\n- ทั้งสองเครื่องใช้ `~/Dropbox/owen-workspace` เดียวกัน\n- `MEMORY.md`, `SOUL.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `memory/` รวมกันทั้งหมด\n- เปิดเครื่องไหน Owen ก็จำได้ทุกอย่างเหมือนกัน\n\nต้องการให้ช่วยสร้าง script หรือทำขั้นตอนไหนเพิ่มเติมไหมครับ? 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":979,"output":580,"cacheRead":47040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48599,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778343750455,"responseId":"064e92479fc22961af34d4de16ae60e0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3207b5b","parentId":"be18c034","timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:25:11.564Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/apinan/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_39---f8548ffd-27c6-4cc0-a7f3-62516bee527e.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/apinan/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_39---f8548ffd-27c6-4cc0-a7f3-62516bee527e.jpg]\n[Image]\nUser text:\n[Telegram ▫️ (@robberzaz) id:1060942816 +2m Sat 2026-05-09 23:24 GMT+7] <media:image>\nDescription:\nThe image shows a macOS terminal window where a user is attempting to run a series of commands. After successfully creating a directory and a symbolic link, the user tries to execute `openclaw onboard --install-daemon`. However, the shell returns the error message \"zsh: command not found: openclaw.\" This indicates that the `openclaw` utility is either not installed on the system or its executable file is not located in any of the directories listed in the user's PATH variable."}],"timestamp":1778343911556}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"[media attached: /home/apinan/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_39---f8548ffd-27c6-4cc0-a7f3-62516bee527e.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/apinan/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_39---f8548ffd-27c6-4cc0-a7f3-62516bee527e.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Absolute and ~ paths only work when they stay inside your allowed file-read boundary; host file:// URLs are blocked. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:1060942816\",\n  \"message_id\": \"8393\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"sender\": \"▫️\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-09 23:24 GMT+7\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"▫️ (1060942816)\",\n  \"id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"name\": \"▫️\",\n  \"username\": \"robberzaz\"\n}\n```\n\n[Image]\nUser text:\n[Telegram ▫️ (@robberzaz) id:1060942816 +2m Sat 2026-05-09 23:24 GMT+7] <media:image>\nDescription:\nThe image shows a macOS terminal window where a user is attempting to run a series of commands. After successfully creating a directory and a symbolic link, the user tries to execute `openclaw onboard --install-daemon`. However, the shell returns the error message \"zsh: command not found: openclaw.\" This indicates that the `openclaw` utility is either not installed on the system or its executable file is not located in any of the directories listed in the user's PATH variable.","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"e3ffbf3a","parentId":"d3207b5b","timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:25:11.569Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"95963079","parentId":"e3ffbf3a","timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:25:30.284Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is getting \"command not found: openclaw\" after running `npm install -g openclaw@latest`. This means npm's global bin directory isn't in the PATH. Let me check what the fix is from the docs.\n\nFrom the docs I read earlier:\n1. Find global npm prefix: `npm prefix -g`\n2. Add `<npm-prefix>/bin` to PATH\n\nThe common issue on macOS with npm global installs is that the path isn't in the shell startup file.\n","thinkingSignature":"6d4fd073f197c625466c84728e525adc9a5deb742cc164a570642700193dae9e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🧑🏼‍💻 ติดตั้งแล้วแต่ PATH ไม่ถูกต้องครับ ต้องเพิ่ม npm global bin เข้าไปใน PATH\n\n**แก้แบบนี้:**\n\n```bash\necho 'export PATH=\"$(npm prefix -g)/bin:$PATH\"' >> ~/.zshrc\nsource ~/.zshrc\nopenclaw --version\n```\n\nถ้าได้ผลลัพธ์แล้ว ค่อยรัน:\n```bash\nopenclaw onboard --install-daemon\n```\n\nลองดูนะครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48686,"output":268,"cacheRead":96,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49050,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778343911569,"responseId":"064e92e85ee0e7f7f7135ee9b4e15af8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7655ea13","parentId":"95963079","timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:26:36.212Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"apaut@Aps-MacBook-Pro ~ % echo 'export PATH=\"$(npm prefix -g)/bin:$PATH\"' >> ~/.zshrc\nsource ~/.zshrc\nopenclaw --version\n\n/Users/apaut/.zshrc:6: command not found: npm\nzsh: command not found: openclaw\napaut@Aps-MacBook-Pro ~ % openclaw onboard --install-daemon\n\nzsh: command not found: openclaw\napaut@Aps-MacBook-Pro ~ %"}],"timestamp":1778343996208}}
