{"type":"message","id":"ac68795a","parentId":"cf59d33b","timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:26:48.120Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that `npm` itself is not found. This means Node.js is not properly installed on the MacBook. Let me check what the recommended installation method is.\n\nThe error says \"command not found: npm\" which means npm isn't installed. The user needs to install Node.js first.\n","thinkingSignature":"7418c6e31e3baf07b033dd81458798753af463f8e406734de9c49e124ce8d8fe"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**npm ยังไม่มีเลย** — ต้องติดตั้ง Node.js ก่อนครับ\n\n**วิธีที่ง่ายที่สุดบน Mac:**\n\n```bash\nbrew install node\n```\n\nรอติดตั้งเสร็จ แล้วค่อยเปิด terminal ใหม่ หรือรัน:\n```bash\nsource ~/.zshrc\nnode -v\nnpm -v\nopenclaw --version\n```\n\nถ้าไม่มี brew ติดตั้งอยู่ ดาวน์โหลด Node.js จากเว็บได้เลย:\nhttps://nodejs.org/ → ดาวน์โหลด LTS กดติดตั้งตามปกติ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8226,"output":289,"cacheRead":40448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48963,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778343996223,"responseId":"064e933eb2f21f9f41300c40be35a62a"}}
