{"type":"message","id":"02ac330e","parentId":"fe42d50e","timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:30:02.785Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that MacBook is running macOS 11 (Big Sur), which is very old. Homebrew says it's Tier 3 and requires building from source because there's no bottle for this old macOS version. Also there's an Xcode Command Line Tools issue.\n\nThe key error is:\n```\nxcrun: error: invalid active developer path (/Library/Developer/CommandLineTools), missing xcrun at: /Library/Developer/CommandLineTools/usr/bin/xcrun\n```\n\nThis means Xcode Command Line Tools are not properly installed. And then:\n```\nError: The following formula cannot be installed from bottle and must be built from source.\n node\nInstall the Command Line Tools:\n xcode-select --install\n\n\n```\n\nThe second error about `node` being a \"permission denied\" command is likely because `node` is being interpreted as a file or alias name rather than a command, which is odd since it should be a directory for the node.rb formula. But the real blocker is that macOS 11 is too old for the current Node.js version, and without proper Command Line Tools, we can't build from source.\n","thinkingSignature":"09a0c7521a68e004812de392f01d7de6902fd36029920668cf2018fddf4c9ad6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n🧑🏼‍💻 ปัญหาสองอย่าง:\n\n1. **Xcode Command Line Tools หายไป** — ต้องติดตั้งก่อน\n2. **macOS 11 เก่ามาก** — Homebrew ไม่มี binary สำเร็จ ต้อง build from source\n\n**แก้ขั้น 1 — ติดตั้ง Command Line Tools:**\n```bash\nsudo rm -rf /Library/Developer/CommandLineTools\nsudo xcode-select --install\n```\n(เลือก Install ในหน้าต่างที่ขึ้นมา รอโหลดเสร็จ)\n\n**แก้ขั้น 2 — หลังติดตั้งเสร็จ ลองอีกครั้ง:**\n```bash\nbrew install node\n```\n\nถ้า brew ยังบอกว่า macOS 11 ไม่รองรับ อาจต้องใช้ **nvm** ติดตั้ง Node เอง:\n\n```bash\ncurl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.0/install.sh | bash\nsource ~/.zshrc\nnvm install 22\nnvm use 22\nnode -v\nnpm -v\nnpm install -g openclaw@latest\nopenclaw --version\n```\n\nลองทำทีละขั้นตอนนะครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":51924,"output":617,"cacheRead":96,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52637,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778344187353,"responseId":"064e93fd144b00bd9fbaa78b64726197"}}
